:08.000Z","msg":"小學二定三年班俾個死肥仔打..<br />\n嗰時嬲到舉起張櫈車左落佢度..<br />\n之後老師罰左我留堂..<br />\n第二日個死肥仔主動同我耍冧say sorry...<br />\n話佢唔應該郁手打我先....<br />\n(覺得應該係佢屋企人同佢講要道歉先..諗返起覺得佢屋企家教幾好)..<br />\n佢耍冧嗰吓我呆左..但不打不相識..小學畢業前都同佢勁frd....<br />\n但舊時小學之後升唔同學校..又唔似而家咁有咁多方法可以聯絡...<br />\n之後就無左聊絡lu...<br />\n所以教唔好還手既教畜收皮啦...dllm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果嗰時我唔還手...可能就成個小學生涯要起校園欺凌下度過...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:56:55.000Z","msg":"真 ，諗起小學好多朋友仔都係不打不相識<br />\n以前同最frd嗰個都係咁樣識<br />\n不過我係死肥仔個角色，就去撩人打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e97ee23cd2b2c9210834c5140ee42fcfffbcdd4","tid":2450180,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:58:11.000Z","msg":"俾人打一撚定要還手 唔夠打都要！就算你報狗佢地都祗會話兩邊都告刁難你，最後等你地怕麻煩和解算<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以還拖好緊要！"},{"pid":"63ce5273092c2eb8778a50be6e77fbeefa85d28a","tid":2450180,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73c614e0b89cf5626cb9b476bb799b15ae164bf3","tid":2450180,"uid":294342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd384eff5472b1a28c9688f89de2de583bca810a","tid":2450180,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f948dcc47f10e53e632ee4164c0168a6499efd8","tid":2450180,"uid":40272,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iX1LtXm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiX1LtXm.jpg&h=0aa4a208&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:41:27.000Z","msg":"13拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:47:49.000Z","msg":"派14巴港女同佢隻揪<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hiftfqy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHiftfqy.jpg&h=af924c2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202